{"tid":1382471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[仁愛堂]何君堯我要你社會賢達都冇得做","createTime":"2019-07-29T13:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:26:44.000Z","uid":6557,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"35a1284958c884cc13a173ba4633f090e3075e76","tid":1382471,"uid":6557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:11:52.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知何君堯阿爸係屯門慈善團體仁愛堂創辦人之一。早兩年立法會選舉都特登返去拍宣傳片，原來佢都做過主席，當年屯門放煙花就係佢搞。<br />\n依家我就要你社會賢達都冇得做！！<br />\n堂堂善團前主席學人鼓吹暴力對唔對得起仁愛兩個字呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家幫我簽左佢，推到仁愛堂同佢割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdtCIB4eJj1qOGIJcpxNvqiMTQyCdN7U1S-NoP29gI7e_PlGQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdtCIB4eJj1qOGIJcpxNvqiMTQyCdN7U1S-NoP29gI7e_PlGQ%2Fviewform&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiie2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=9247c8fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdtCIB4eJj1qOGIJcpxNvqiMTQyCdN7U1S-NoP29gI7e_PlGQ/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"228c50776b8c384d62bc343ed9106698ac0c557b","tid":1382471,"uid":6557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9383dfd6323f7b281d3ed42cee178946e643e27b","tid":1382471,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:30.000Z","msg":"「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovuS</a>"},{"pid":"0d5e2c2a7242ac359f3210c7e13af207740329ed","tid":1382471,"uid":6557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa169ae7c15d3eaa58028cb2bcd2251bd4d92ad","tid":1382471,"uid":150083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite